<br>
Tomorrow evening, Deus Factum has PoH booked. Tomorrow might also be the first day of the &quot;New and Improved&quot; Plane of Hate from the test server.<br>
<br>
Deus Factum can clear Hate, with Inny up, in 5 hours. But tomorrow might be a whole new ball of wax. Who knows what it will be like and if we will be able to tackle Inny? Not us, we have no idea what to expect.<br>
<br>
We are planning to insert a couple groups tonight - hope that is OK with KEG (let me know if you have any timing concerns) - to be sure we have a cleric at the SS and a Rogue up there for CR. Sounds like break-in for the new PoH is a rough insertion.<br>
<br>
So... DF has always been VERY good about calling in the current BB, but this is a strange situation. Sounds like the Epic stuff will fall off the MOBs we can easily handle (new named spawns) and Inny himself drops a whole new loot table and the whole &quot;BB for Epic Items&quot; wouldn't make sense - if we need help with Inny we can make the call, but there probably won't be any epic loot for the BB.<br>
<br>
What are people thoughts? I want to recommend we just become the first guild to guinea pig the new PoH on The Rathe and we'll post what we find Wednesday and more steps can be taken then...<br>
<br>
Titus Divinitus<br>
Deus Factum<br>
<br>
